    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh wait, amoxicillin is prescription only in australia so i cant just get that at the chemist. do you think i could just use some extra strength neosporin or maybe some hydrogen peroxide instead? would that be just as effective for stopping an infection if i can't get the pills?",
